Stefan,

It's a bug, and there is a fix for this in the latest CVS
near the end of the QueryParser.jj file:

      // avoid boosting null queries, such as those caused by stop words
      if (q != null) {
        q.setBoost(f);
      }

Kind regards,
Ype


